# Project Overview
This is a modern cloud development monorepo seed project that demonstrates best practices for:
- AWS cloud development
- Infrastructure as Code with Pulumi
- Monorepo development with Nx
- CI/CD with GitHub Actions and NxCloud

# Core Principles
- Follow clean code principles and consistent formatting
- Maintain clear separation of concerns
- Ensure proper error handling and logging
- Write comprehensive tests for all components
- Document architecture decisions and component usage

# Development Workflow
- Use feature branches and pull requests
- Ensure CI passes before merging
- Follow semantic versioning for releases